{"tid":2339463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［又到聖誕］施永青 聖誕快樂！","createTime":"2020-12-24T15:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T21:04:05.000Z","uid":307607,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d606b90148b997bc23d0d381f2c5956ca888b83d","tid":2339463,"uid":307607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqjYHHp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqjYHHp.png&h=43fd3d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過中原地產創辦人施永青對「聖誕」就有HardFeeling，《壹週刊》報道，施永青一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「我最憎就是聖誕！」，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n依家施永青財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！<br />\n<br />\n聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0427d19df703b448c5c6b5045ee7abeaf82a9f8d","tid":2339463,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:03:10.000Z","msg":"X你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5fe4a8427f5c5ec1102c04dbaeecc95f5213aa","tid":2339463,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:07:00.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂呀屍永青"},{"pid":"800e42d2941f9453d0cafe828bc98bc3a1cbcb35","tid":2339463,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂呀施永青<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54eb7de12d0c1ccfc8874faec02ee57e5f7cde04","tid":2339463,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SvwoTSE.jpg\"